rooms.Name: Sloping Hallway
rooms.Description:
This hallway branches from the room and begins to slope downward.  The slope
is rather steep and you must walk carefully to avoid falling.  Also, the stone
walls and floor seem to be darker, almost more sinister in nature.  It's hard
to believe that anything could be worse than some of the things you've already
seen.

rooms.Name: Sloping hallway
rooms.Description:
The hallway continues to slope down toward the west.  Some thick, grey
gelatinous material covers the wall on one side.  It almost looks like brain
matter.  You shudder at the thought and keep walking.

rooms.Name: T in sloping hallway
rooms.Description:
Here the hallway flattens out and the hallway continues in the north/south
direction.  You hear what sounds like deep moans of sadness from the south.
The hallway north leads into darkness.

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
rooms.Description:
THis hallway is very very dark.  Even compared to the rest of the tower, this
darkness is unusual.  It almost seems as if the stones themselves are radiating
the darkness.  Something tells you the Crown Jewels MUST be this way.

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
rooms.Description:
This dark hallway finally shows some signs of life.  To the north, you can see
some flicker lights that look like torches or lamps.  How in the world can
the guards see in this cursed darkness?

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
rooms.Description: You are in a hallway that continues north/south.

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
rooms.Description: You are in a hallway that continues north/south.

rooms.Name: Small circular room
rooms.Description:
You have entered a circular room that is about 20 feet in diameter.  There
seems to be no ceiling as the roof is completely out of sight.  Bright light
flickers from the exit to the northwest.  An extremely narrow exit leads to
the northeast into darkness.  A sign hangs on the wall here.

ExtraDescs.Description:
"You can unlock any door if you only have the key."
                           -----Mrs. Jonathan Brisby

rooms.Name: Another T intersection
rooms.Description:
Here, you can go any of three directions.  You can return to the north or
see where the corridor heading east/west leads.

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
rooms.Description:
This corridor is getting kinda warm.  Heat rushes at you from a direction
you can't be certain of.  You're pretty sure it's not coming from the
intersection you just came from.

rooms.Name: a hallway in the Tower
Confusing, twisting corridor
rooms.Description:
You are in a corridor that looks exactly like the one you were in 5 minutes
ago, which looks like the same one you were in 10 minutes ago.  You are
getting very confused.  The torchlight dances wildly off the walls casting
strange shadows.  Will this cursed corridor never end???

rooms.Name: Very cold hallway
rooms.Description:
There is a very, VERY cold wind blowing down this hallway from the west.
It chills you to the bone and is absolutely relentless.  You have serious
second thoughts about continuing west.  Let's go back east where it is warm.

rooms.Name: Meat freezer
rooms.Description:
The t-t-temperature here must-t-t be b-b-below f-fr-fr-freezing.  You m-must
b-b-be in the some t-typ-pe of storage area.  Brrrr.  Did I mention it's
c-c-c-cold.  You c-can f-feel your flesh fr-freezing.  B-B-Better g-get out-t
now.
